Relationship between Neha and Rohit is that of a married couple. Initially, Neha denies the fact that her husband is dead, but later accepts the reality.
Sakshi falls in love with Rohit's impersonator, Vicky. However, she is also related to Rohit's wife Neha as they both married Rohit's brothers.
Vicky poses as Rohit for the sake of Neha and Sakshi's family. Later, he realizes his debt to Rohit and returns.
Bhanwarlal intends to kill Rohit but mistakenly kills someone else. This incident results in Vicky's debt towards Rohit.
Relationship between Sakshi and Neha is that of a sister-in-law and a married sister, respectively.
Sakshi's uncle wants her to marry his brother.
Similarly, Sakshi's aunt tries to have her marry their brother.
